Ability Basics




Ability Use Counts
　
Each ability can be used a set amount of times.
There are passive abilities that can increase this use count.


Effects that Prevent Use Count Consumption
　
There are conditions under which certain abilities' use counts will not decrease after use.
　
While effects that prevent use count consumption are active, the applicable ability's use count will become green.
*Abilities subject to effects that prevent use count consumption are as follows:
　• Initially acquired abilities
　• Abilities acquired at crystal STR LV 20
　• Additional abilities


Abilities without Use Counts
　
EX Abilities do not have use counts.
You can use them as many times as you wish after the recast gauge fills.
